Definition: law) the principle that an act done at a later time is deemed by law to have occurred at an earlier time
Example: his attorney argued for the relation back of the amended complaint to the time the initial complaint was filed
Synonyms: relation, legal_principle, noun, group, law, c, the, principle, that, an, act, done, at, a, later, time, is, deemed, by, to, have, occurred, earlier, his, attorney, argued, for, back, of, amended, complaint, initial, was, filed
Category: noun.cognition
